Available Tools: get_lab_results | get_latest_results | get_result_history | download_report
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "patient_id": "string", "test_type": "string", "from_date": "string" }
Response Schema: { "results": [{ "test": "string", "value": number, "unit": "string", "reference_range": "string", "status": "normal|high|low" }] }
---
Question: Obtain the thyroid function panel for patient P-1045.
Call: { "func_call": "get_latest_results", "patient_id": "P-1045", "test_type": "TSH Panel", "from_date": "" }
Response: { "results": [{ "test": "TSH", "value": 2.5, "unit": "mIU/L", "reference_range": "0.4-4.0", "status": "normal" }, { "test": "Free T4", "value": 1.2, "unit": "ng/dL", "reference_range": "0.8-1.8", "status": "normal" }, { "test": "Free T3", "value": 3.1, "unit": "pg/mL", "reference_range": "2.3-4.2", "status": "normal" }] }

